Title: PLUVIA ROOF OUTLET C SHT FST FLNGE 12L/S
Description: Reducing the number of roof outlets and stacks required, the Geberit Pluvia 12L/S roof outlet offers fast draining in large roof areas. Unlike conventional drainage systems, Pluvia allows the pipe system to completely fill with water, encouraging negative pressure for fast suction removal. This makes Pluvia powerfully effective and improves efficiency, reducing costs as well as planning and construction effort. Suitable for use in insulated and uninsulated roofs, this system is also suitable for installation on green roofs.

Title: Geberit roof outlet with fastening flange for roof foils 25ltr/s
Description: Capable of draining 25L per second, this Geberit roof outlet with 90mm HDPE connection and fastening flange for 4mm roof foils is part of the reliable Pluvia roof drainage system.
